query:
/*+ NoHashJoin(n ci) NoHashJoin(ci n mi) NoMergeJoin(ci mi n t) NoMergeJoin(ci mi n t mc) NoHashJoin(ci mc mi n t an) NoHashJoin(an ci mc mi n t cn) NoHashJoin(an ci cn mc mi n t rt) NoHashJoin(an ci cn it mc mi n rt t chn) */ select min(n.name) AS voicing_actress,
min(t.title) AS jap_engl_voiced_movie
from name AS n
inner join cast_info AS ci
on n.id = ci.person_id AND n.gender = 'f' AND n.name like '%Conn,%' AND ci.note IN ('(producer)',
'(voice)',
'(uncredited)',
'(as Terri Colombino)')
inner join movie_info AS mi
on mi.movie_id = ci.movie_id AND mi.info IS NOT NULL AND ( mi.info like 'Japan:%200%' OR mi.info like 'USA:%200%')
inner join title AS t
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2006
inner join movie_companies AS mc
on t.id = mc.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND mc.movie_id = ci.movie_id
inner join aka_name AS an
on ci.person_id = an.person_id AND n.id = an.person_id
inner join company_name AS cn
on cn.id = mc.company_id AND cn.country_code = '[us]'
inner join role_type AS rt
on rt.id = ci.role_id AND rt.role = 'actress'
inner join info_type AS it
on it.id = mi.info_type_id AND it.info = 'release dates'
inner join char_name AS chn
on chn.id = ci.person_role_id;
